-- MOVES-RSA Insurance names Steve Lewis CEO for UK, Western Europe
-- By Ramkumar Iyer in Bangalore
-- Thu Jun 26, 2014 02:45PM EDT
-- None



June 26 (Reuters) - RSA Insurance Group Plc <RSA.L> appointed Steve Lewis as chief executive for the UK and Western Europe, effective Jan. 1, 2015.

Lewis will replace Adrian Brown, who will remain in his current role until Aug. 31. In his new role, Lewis will be responsible for the company's RSA and MORE TH>N brands in the UK, the 123.ie brand in Ireland, and businesses across Western Europe.